## Bridge to Neural NLP {.unnumbered}

By the end of this lab, students should be able to explain how cleaned SEC text could later become:

1. a Bag-of-Words or TF-IDF matrix
2. an input to a neural text classifier
3. a source corpus for embeddings or language modeling

This matters because later Module 1 work does not start from raw text again. It builds directly on the preprocessing discipline established here.


